      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Engine.Core.SimulationEngine",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Engine.Core.SimulationEngine.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">The central singleton that drives the entire simulation.\nIt maintains the device registry, owns the tick-based time model, and\nmanages the priority queue of in-flight packets.</p>\n<p>\nEvery call to <xref href=\"Engine.Core.SimulationEngine.Tick\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> advances the simulation by one step:\nthe tick counter is incremented, wall-clock delta time is measured,\nall subscribers to <xref href=\"Engine.Core.SimulationEngine.TickEvent\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> are notified, and any packets\nwhose <xref href=\"Engine.Packets.Packet.ArrivalTick\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> has been reached are dequeued and\ndispatched to their <xref href=\"Engine.Packets.Packet.NextHop\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> device.\n</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
