      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Engine.Devices.Device",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Engine.Devices.Device.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Abstract base class for all devices in the simulation network.\nA device has a unique identity and a position in 2D space.\nWhen it receives a packet it either forwards it (if it is not the\nintended recipient) or accepts and processes it.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Engine.Devices.EmitterDevice.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/Engine.Devices.EmitterDevice.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Engine.Devices.EmitterDevice",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Engine.Devices.EmitterDevice.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A device that receives command packets from the hub and applies a boolean\nstate to itself (e.g. turning an actuator on or off).\nWhen an accepted packet carries a <code>bool</code> payload the device updates\nits <xref href=\"Engine.Devices.EmitterDevice.State\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> accordingly.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Engine.Devices.GeneratorDevice.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/Engine.Devices.GeneratorDevice.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Engine.Devices.GeneratorDevice",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Engine.Devices.GeneratorDevice.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A device that periodically generates sensor-like data packets and routes\nthem toward the hub. An internal tick counter increments on every engine\ntick and resets to zero after it reaches <xref href=\"Engine.Devices.GeneratorDevice.GenFrequencyTicks\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>;\na packet is emitted only at that reset moment, so exactly one packet is\nsent per <xref href=\"Engine.Devices.GeneratorDevice.GenFrequencyTicks\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> ticks.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Engine.Devices.HubDevice.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/Engine.Devices.HubDevice.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Engine.Devices.HubDevice",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Engine.Devices.HubDevice.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Represents the central hub (gateway) device of the simulation network.\nThe hub is the designated destination for packets generated by\n<xref href=\"Engine.Devices.GeneratorDevice\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> instances and the root of the network topology.\nIt is registered as the singleton hub inside <xref href=\"Engine.Core.SimulationEngine\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>\nwhen added to the simulation.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Engine.Devices.yml",
