    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Engine.Packets.ConfirmationPacket.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/Engine.Packets.ConfirmationPacket.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Engine.Packets.ConfirmationPacket",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Engine.Packets.ConfirmationPacket.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A special packet that is automatically generated and sent back to the\noriginal sender when a packet with <xref href=\"Engine.Packets.Packet.NeedConfirmation\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>\nset to <code>true</code> is successfully delivered.\nThe payload contains the <xref href=\"System.Guid\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> bytes of the confirmed packet,\nallowing the sender to correlate the acknowledgement with the original\ntransmission.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Engine.Packets.Packet.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/Engine.Packets.Packet.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Engine.Packets.Packet",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Engine.Packets.Packet.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Represents a unit of data travelling through the simulation network.\nA packet knows its originator (<xref href=\"Engine.Packets.Packet.From\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>), its intended\ndestination (<xref href=\"Engine.Packets.Packet.To\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>), and the <xref href=\"Engine.Packets.Packet.NextHop\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> device it\nwill be delivered to on the next simulation tick.\nTravel time is expressed in engine ticks via <xref href=\"Engine.Packets.Packet.TicksToTravel\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>,\nand each hop decrements the <xref href=\"Engine.Packets.Packet.TTL\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> counter — a packet that\nreaches zero TTL is silently dropped.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Engine.Packets.PacketData.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/Engine.Packets.PacketData.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Engine.Packets.PacketData",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Engine.Packets.PacketData.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Carries the application-level payload of a <xref href=\"Engine.Packets.Packet\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.\nThe <xref href=\"Engine.Packets.PacketData.Data\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> property is intentionally untyped so that any\nvalue (sensor readings, command flags, raw bytes, etc.) can be transported\nwithout the engine imposing a schema.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Engine.Packets.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/Engine.Packets.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Engine.Packets",
      "Summary": null
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Engine.Routers.PacketRouter.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/Engine.Routers.PacketRouter.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Engine.Routers.PacketRouter",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Engine.Routers.PacketRouter.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Implements a flooding broadcast routing strategy.\nWhen asked to route a packet from a given device, the router queries\n<xref href=\"Engine.Core.SimulationEngine\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> for all devices visible to that device and\nenqueues a cloned copy of the packet addressed to each of them.\nThis is the sole routing mechanism currently used by the engine.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Engine.Routers.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/Engine.Routers.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Engine.Routers",
      "Summary": null
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Engine.Statistics.SimulationStatistics.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/Engine.Statistics.SimulationStatistics.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Engine.Statistics.SimulationStatistics",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Engine.Statistics.SimulationStatistics.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A singleton that listens to <xref href=\"Engine.Core.SimulationEngine\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> events and\naccumulates simulation metrics.</p>\n<p>\nExtensibility: add a new <xref href=\"Engine.Statistics.StatMetric\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> to <xref href=\"Engine.Statistics.SimulationStatistics.Metrics\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>\nand subscribe to any <xref href=\"Engine.Core.SimulationEngine\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> event to populate it.\nThe <xref href=\"Engine.Statistics.SimulationStatistics.Updated\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> event is raised after every change so UI layers\ncan re-render reactively without polling.\n</p>\n<p>\nEvery tick a <xref href=\"Engine.Statistics.TickSnapshot\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> is appended to <xref href=\"Engine.Statistics.SimulationStatistics.History\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>\n(capped at <xref href=\"Engine.Statistics.SimulationStatistics.MaxHistoryLength\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> entries) for time-series charts.\n</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Engine.Statistics.StatMetric.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/Engine.Statistics.StatMetric.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Engine.Statistics.StatMetric",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Engine.Statistics.StatMetric.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A single observable metric tracked by <xref href=\"Engine.Statistics.SimulationStatistics\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.\nUI layers bind to <xref href=\"Engine.Statistics.StatMetric.DisplayValue\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> and listen to\n<xref href=\"Engine.Statistics.SimulationStatistics.Updated\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> for re-renders.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Engine.Statistics.TickSnapshot.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/Engine.Statistics.TickSnapshot.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Engine.Statistics.TickSnapshot",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Engine.Statistics.TickSnapshot.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">An immutable snapshot of all plottable metric values captured at the end\nof a single engine tick. Stored in the <xref href=\"Engine.Statistics.SimulationStatistics\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>\nhistory ring-buffer and consumed by the chart UI.</p>\n"
    },
